="00:38.388" end="00:38.806">は</span><span begin="00:38.806" end="00:39.403">いつ</span><span begin="00:39.403" end="00:39.659">の</span><span begin="00:39.641" end="00:39.960">間に</span><span begin="00:39.960" end="00:40.562">か</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们在不知不觉间</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">bo ku ta chi wa i tsu no ma ni ka</span></p><p begin="00:40.831" end="00:44.153" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:40.831" end="00:41.793">常識</span><span begin="00:41.793" end="00:42.209">に</span><span begin="00:42.209" end="00:43.276">溺れ</span><span begin="00:43.276" end="00:43.776">て</span><span begin="00:43.776" end="00:44.153">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">沉溺常识之中</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">jo u shi ki ni o bo re te ta</span></p><p begin="00:44.391" end="00:47.600" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:44.391" end="00:45.232">朝起き</span><span begin="00:45.232" end="00:45.616">て</span><span begin="00:45.616" end="00:46.199">寝癖</span><span begin="00:46.199" end="00:46.975">直し</span><span begin="00:46.975" end="00:47.600">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">早上起床整理睡乱的头发</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a sa o ki te ne ku se na o shi te</span></p><p begin="00:47.589" end="00:50.936" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:47.589" end="00:49.063">7:30</span><span begin="00:49.063" end="00:49.612">駅に</span><span begin="00:49.612" end="00:50.253">向かっ</span><span begin="00:50.253" end="00:50.936">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在七点半去车站</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">shi chi ji ha n e ki ni mu ka tte</span></p><p begin="00:51.114" end="00:54.213" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:51.114" end="00:51.791">歩い</span><span begin="00:51.791" end="00:51.991">て</span><span begin="00:51.991" end="00:52.746">た</span><span begin="00:52.746" end="00:53.722">生活</span><span begin="00:53.722" end="00:54.213">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就这样走过的生活</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a ru i te ta se i ka tsu ga</span></p><p begin="00:54.213" end="00:59.228" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:54.213" end="00:55.209">なんだ</span><span begin="00:55.209" end="00:55.991">か</span><span begin="00:55.991" end="00:56.805">懐か</span><span begin="00:56.805" end="00:57.422">し</span><span begin="00:57.422" end="00:58.088">く</span><span begin="00:58.088" end="00:59.228">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不知为何也有些怀念</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">na n da ka na tsu ka shi ku te</span></p><p begin="00:59.093" end="01:02.720" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:59.093" end="00:59.532">また</span><span begin="00:59.532" end="01:00.723">明日</span><span begin="01:00.723" end="01:01.031">も</span><span begin="01:01.031" end="01:02.720">ずっと</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直坚信明天也是</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ma ta a shi ta mo zu tto</span></p><p begin="01:01.929" end="01:06.352" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:01.929" end="01:02.217">「い</span><span begin="01:02.217" end="01:02.590">つ</span><span begin="01:02.590" end="01:03.047">も</span><span begin="01:03.047" end="01:03.757">の</span><span begin="01:03.757" end="01:06.352">朝が」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「平常的早上」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">「i tsu mo no a sa ga」</span></p><p begin="01:05.975" end="01:09.534" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:05.975" end="01:06.478">その</span><span begin="01:06.478" end="01:07.140">先</span><span begin="01:07.140" end="01:07.507">も</span><span begin="01:07.507" end="01:09.534">きっと</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">明天也一定会有</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">so no sa ki mo ki tto</span></p><p begin="01:08.812" end="01:13.424" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:08.812" end="01:09.400">「変わ</span><span begin="01:09.400" end="01:09.880">ら</span><span begin="01:09.880" end="01:10.606">ない</span><span begin="01:10.606" end="01:11.629">日々</span><span begin="01:11.629" end="01:13.424">が」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「是不变的日子」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">「ka wa ra na i hi bi ga」</span></p><p begin="01:12.900" end="01:18.090" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:12.900" end="01:13.668">当たり</span><span begin="01:13.668" end="01:14.676">前に</span><span begin="01:14.676" end="01:15.483">来る</span><span begin="01:15.483" end="01:16.048">と</span><span begin="01:16.048" end="01:17.401">思っ</span><span begin="01:17.401" end="01:17.638">て</span><span begin="01:17.638" end="01:18.090">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">到来也是理所应当的吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">a ta ri ma e ni ku ru to o mo tte ta</span></p><p begin="01:18.090" end="01:21.273" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:18.090" end="01:18.951">「教え</span><span begin="01:18.951" end="01:19.242">て</span><span begin="01:19.242" end="01:19.611">よ</span><span begin="01:19.611" end="01:20.102">明日</span><span begin="01:20.102" end="01:20.306">の</span><span begin="01:20.306" end="01:21.273">天気」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">「告诉我吧 明天的天气」</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">「o shi e te yo a shi ta no te n ki」</span></p><p begin="01:21.273" end="01:24.833" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:21.273" end="01:21.849">必死</span><span begin="01:21.849" end="01:22.395">に</span><span begin="01:22.395" end="01:23.309">常識</span><span begin="01:23.309" end="01:23.928">翳し</span><span begin="01:23.928" end="01:24.305">て</span><span begin="01:24.305" end="01:24.833">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">拼命地以「常识」为盾</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">hi sshi ni jo u shi ki e i shi te ta</span></p><p begin="01:24.833" end="01:26.392" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:24.833" end="01:25.338">大人</span><span begin="01:25.338" end="01:25.995">達</span><span begin="01:25.995" end="01:26.392">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" x